00:17:16,560 --> 00:17:17,240
Yeah.

275
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,400
Haa...

276
00:17:28,640 --> 00:17:29,680
Another sigh.

277
00:17:30,080 --> 00:17:31,440
Good thing I didn't count.

278
00:17:31,440 --> 00:17:33,640
I'd run out of fingers and toes.

279
00:17:34,080 --> 00:17:35,400
I'm worried about Lada.

280
00:17:36,080 --> 00:17:37,080
I'm worried too,

281
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:38,160
but she's made her choice.

282
00:17:38,160 --> 00:17:39,080
What can we do?

283
00:17:39,080 --> 00:17:40,280
That's not it.

284
00:17:42,800 --> 00:17:44,840
I mean, I'm worried about that, too,

285
00:17:45,600 --> 00:17:47,400
I don't want her to get hurt.

286
00:17:47,840 --> 00:17:48,960
But

287
00:17:49,040 --> 00:17:50,920
there's something even more concerning.

288
00:17:51,560 --> 00:17:52,560
What is it?

289
00:17:58,520 --> 00:18:00,400
Have the ad crew left yet?

290
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:01,880
Not yet, ma'am.

291
00:18:01,880 --> 00:18:02,960
But before coming up here,

292
00:18:02,960 --> 00:18:04,080
I saw them still working.

293
00:18:04,080 --> 00:18:05,520
They should be finishing up soon.

294
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:13,480
Earn, are you done changing yet?

295
00:18:13,680 --> 00:18:14,720
Not yet.

296
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:16,160
Just a moment.

297
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,040
If you're done,

298
00:18:18,080 --> 00:18:19,600
just toss the clothes out.

299
00:18:19,600 --> 00:18:21,320
I really need to use the bathroom.

300
00:18:21,360 --> 00:18:22,840
Oh, okay, okay, okay.

301
00:18:42,240 --> 00:18:43,240
Oh!

302
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:44,400
Doctor!

303
00:18:44,440 --> 00:18:45,640
What is this?

304
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,120
-You startled me.
-Why?

305
00:18:47,360 --> 00:18:48,240
Why?

306
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:49,520
You startled me!

307
00:18:49,920 --> 00:18:52,040
I've wanted to do this for a long time,

308
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:53,640
but in front of others,

309
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:55,640
I was afraid you'd be embarrassed.

310
00:19:00,200 --> 00:19:01,480
Afraid I'd be embarrassed

311
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:03,760
or are you just not brave enough?

312
00:19:05,360 --> 00:19:06,280
Then let's go.

313
00:19:06,280 --> 00:19:07,360
Where to?

314
00:19:08,360 --> 00:19:09,400
To kiss you

315
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:11,560
in front of the crew

316
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:13,040
and announce that

317
00:19:13,200 --> 00:19:15,720
we're a couple!

318
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:17,760
Earn!

319
00:19:20,160 --> 00:19:21,160
No way.

320
00:19:21,240 --> 00:19:22,240
Why not?

321
00:19:23,400 --> 00:19:24,400
Why not?

322
00:19:24,400 --> 00:19:26,120
Not without payment first.

323
00:19:26,120 --> 00:19:27,160
Here.

324
00:19:27,600 --> 00:19:28,880
One million,

325
00:19:29,280 --> 00:19:30,520
two million,

326
00:19:31,240 --> 00:19:32,280
three million.

327
00:19:32,840 --> 00:19:33,720
Is that enough?

328
00:19:33,720 --> 00:19:34,720
Not enough.

329
00:19:37,360 --> 00:19:38,440
Still not enough?

330
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:48,640
Certainly, Earn.

331
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:06,360
LOUNGE

332
00:20:17,000 --> 00:20:18,000
Mother.

333
00:20:23,440 --> 00:20:24,440
Mother.

334
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:26,600
This is

335
00:20:27,280 --> 00:20:28,280
Earn,

336
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:30,760
our hospital's new presenter.

337
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,720
Hello.

338
00:20:35,720 --> 00:20:36,680
Hello.

339
00:20:37,760 --> 00:20:39,720
We just finished the commercial shoot.

340
00:20:39,840 --> 00:20:41,760
There's just a bit of interviewing left.

341
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,080
Have you eaten yet, Mother?

342
00:20:44,360 --> 00:20:46,120
We can go grab something to eat after.

343
00:20:46,120 --> 00:20:47,120
No, thank you.

344
00:20:49,120 --> 00:20:50,280
I have no appetite.

345
00:20:53,560 --> 00:20:55,560
Excuse me, Doctor, we're ready for you.

346
00:20:56,360 --> 00:20:57,360
Alright.

347
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:58,720
Thank you.

348
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:01,600
I'll go finish the interview then.

349
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:03,000
Alright.

350
00:21:04,640 --> 00:21:05,640
Oh.

351
00:21:05,680 --> 00:21:07,040
Actually, I'll catch up.

352
00:21:07,120 --> 00:21:09,280
I think I left my bag in the room.

353
00:21:11,240 --> 00:21:13,000
-See you in a bit.
-Yes.

354
00:21:14,440 --> 00:21:15,640
Right this way.

355
00:21:23,960 --> 00:21:25,360
After I helped your mother,

356
00:21:26,480 --> 00:21:29,280
you repay me by breaking your promise?

357
00:21:31,160 --> 00:21:32,160
Why?

358
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,400
Are you desperately in need of money

359
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:37,400
that you had to return to my daughter?

360
00:21:43,240 --> 00:21:44,240
I love her.

361
00:21:48,000 --> 00:21:49,640
It's up to you to believe it or not,

362
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:50,800
but it’s the truth.

363
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:54,200
Even if she is penniless,

364
00:21:54,200 --> 00:21:55,920
I would still be with her.

365
00:21:58,120 --> 00:21:59,120
Clever.

366
00:22:00,040 --> 00:22:01,280
Using love as an excuse

367
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:04,760
to betray without guilt, huh?

368
00:22:08,520 --> 00:22:10,280
I never broke my promise.

369
00:22:11,320 --> 00:22:13,520
I really did leave her.

370
00:22:14,880 --> 00:22:15,960
You already see that

371
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:17,560
I stayed away for two years,

372
00:22:17,560 --> 00:22:20,040
never coming near her.

373
00:22:20,040 --> 00:22:21,360
Then why are you back?

374
00:22:22,320 --> 00:22:23,560
Because you lied to me.

375
00:22:24,680 --> 00:22:28,120
You said our love would never be real,

376
00:22:28,360 --> 00:22:30,200
that things would happen naturally.

377
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:32,000
But it's not true.

378
00:22:33,080 --> 00:22:34,200
Because today,

379
00:22:34,320 --> 00:22:36,520
she's not with Dr. Wisanu.

380
00:22:38,560 --> 00:22:39,760
If I had known,

381
00:22:40,120 --> 00:22:41,440
I would have found another way

382
00:22:41,440 --> 00:22:42,360
to help my mother

383
00:22:42,400 --> 00:22:44,200
and never made that promise to you.

384
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:45,880
That's why today,

385
00:22:49,240 --> 00:22:51,200
I’m taking back my love.

386
00:24:09,760 --> 00:24:10,840
Here you go.

387
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:13,000
-Take your medicine.
-Thank you.

388
00:24:14,040 --> 00:24:15,160
Here.

389
00:24:25,240 --> 00:24:26,240
Thank you.

390
00:24:29,320 --> 00:24:31,280
I told you to rest more,

391
00:24:31,760 --> 00:24:33,040
but you never listen.

392
00:24:33,400 --> 00:24:35,240
You work so hard that you got sick.

393
00:24:35,280 --> 00:24:36,360
You're so stubborn.

394
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:39,360
If I weren't diligent,

395
00:24:40,120 --> 00:24:42,480
would our hospital have grown this big?

396
00:24:44,120 --> 00:24:46,160
Or would you prefer just a small clinic?

397
00:24:51,840 --> 00:24:54,040
If it means having more time with you,

398
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:57,000
a small clinic would be enough.

399
00:24:59,760 --> 00:25:00,480
Really?

400
00:25:00,520 --> 00:25:01,520
Yes.

401
00:25:06,440 --> 00:25:08,080
I will pass the medical exams

402
00:25:08,800 --> 00:25:11,040
and help you and Father with the work,

403
00:25:11,840 --> 00:25:13,800
so you both won't have to be so tired.

404
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:20,360
That sounds wonderful.

405
00:25:21,160 --> 00:25:22,200
Do you like the idea?

406
00:25:32,480 --> 00:25:34,440
What did the mail say? Did she pass?

407
00:25:38,160 --> 00:25:39,160
She passed!

408
00:25:40,080 --> 00:25:41,200
You scared me!

409
00:25:43,840 --> 00:25:45,560
She passed the skin medical school exams.

410
00:25:45,600 --> 00:25:47,720
There were so many competitors,

411
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:51,320
and she scored among the top!

412
00:25:52,560 --> 00:25:54,440
Lada never disappoints me.

413
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:56,080
Amazing like her mother.

414
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:58,560
Absolutely, you couldn't be more right.

415
00:26:10,760 --> 00:26:11,760
Come in.

416
00:26:15,560 --> 00:26:16,720
Celeb Today wants to

417
00:26:16,760 --> 00:26:18,360
schedule an interview with you ma'am.

418
00:26:29,320 --> 00:26:30,320
Alright,

419
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,160
ask them for the date.

420
00:26:34,000 --> 00:26:34,920
Yes, ma'am.

421
00:26:38,120 --> 00:26:39,280
Are you hungry?

422
00:26:39,760 --> 00:26:41,480
Just tell me what you want to eat.

423
00:26:41,800 --> 00:26:42,840
I'm hungry,

424
00:26:42,880 --> 00:26:44,440
but I want to go home and eat.

425
00:26:45,440 --> 00:26:46,440
As you wish.

426
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:56,840
Is something bothering you?

427
00:27:01,880 --> 00:27:03,160
Do you think

428
00:27:04,320 --> 00:27:06,720
your mother will accept us?

429
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,040
Oh, is that all?

430
00:27:11,120 --> 00:27:12,200
Don't worry about it.

431
00:27:12,240 --> 00:27:13,920
It's not a big deal these days,

432
00:27:14,160 --> 00:27:15,160
hmm?

433
00:27:23,360 --> 00:27:24,720
My mom loves me,

434
00:27:24,760 --> 00:27:26,440
and she'll love you too.

435
00:27:27,360 --> 00:27:28,880
She'll understand our love.

436
00:27:35,520 --> 00:27:36,520
Let's go.

437
00:27:47,680 --> 00:27:48,640
Of course it's

438
00:27:48,680 --> 00:27:50,080
Fried Boiled Egg with Tamarind Sauce

439
00:27:50,080 --> 00:27:51,600
and Stir-fried Glass Noodles.

440
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:55,480
At least we have clear soup.

441
00:27:57,120 --> 00:27:58,360
Are you sure it's edible?

442
00:27:59,040 --> 00:28:00,320
It's your first time making it,

443
00:28:00,320 --> 00:28:01,920
and I don't want to die.

444
00:28:04,560 --> 00:28:05,840
You're underestimate me

445
00:28:10,840 --> 00:28:12,520
Here, taste it and see.

446
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:13,960
If you're going to die,

447
00:28:13,960 --> 00:28:15,160
you'll die in front of me.

448
00:28:19,440 --> 00:28:20,440
Oops.

449
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:23,920
Oops.

450
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:29,080
Sorry!

451
00:28:29,520 --> 00:28:30,560
I'll stop teasing.

452
00:28:36,320 --> 00:28:37,320
Hmm.

453
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:39,160
Is that a nod of approval?

454
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,680
It's a nod of

455
00:28:40,680 --> 00:28:42,200
"I'm definitely going to die."

456
00:28:42,400 --> 00:28:46,280
Geez, don't tease me like that!

457
00:28:46,640 --> 00:28:48,640
Okay, okay, I'll stop teasing.

458
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:51,320
I was just joking.

459
00:28:51,760 --> 00:28:52,760
Okay.

460
00:30:44,000 --> 00:30:45,120
Earn.

461
00:30:45,360 --> 00:30:46,360
Oh, Doctor!

462
00:30:47,000 --> 00:30:47,960
You're up already?

463
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:49,000
Yeah.

464
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:51,160
What are you doing?

465
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:53,280
Morning.

466
00:30:53,400 --> 00:30:54,400
Morning.

467
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,840
I'm ironing your shirt

468
00:30:59,840 --> 00:31:01,640
so you can wear it to work.

469
00:31:03,840 --> 00:31:04,800
But

470
00:31:06,240 --> 00:31:07,920
I'm not working today.

471
00:31:09,480 --> 00:31:10,480
Hmm,

472
00:31:10,480 --> 00:31:12,160
why not? Are you slacking off?

473
00:31:14,440 --> 00:31:16,080
I'm not slacking off,

474
00:31:16,440 --> 00:31:18,800
but I don't have any rounds today.

475
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:21,400
Ah, you don't have rounds.

476
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:22,840
In that case,

477
00:31:22,840 --> 00:31:24,320
once I finish ironing this,

478
00:31:24,360 --> 00:31:26,600
I'll go make breakfast for you, okay?

479
00:31:29,440 --> 00:31:31,080
You don't have to go anywhere.

480
00:31:34,600 --> 00:31:36,600
Don't be too nice to me.

481
00:31:37,840 --> 00:31:38,840
Why not?

482
00:31:40,440 --> 00:31:41,720
I might fall even more for you.

483
00:31:42,880 --> 00:31:44,040
Geez,

484
00:31:44,080 --> 00:31:45,240
you're so sweet first thing

485
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,200
in the morning.

486
00:31:46,240 --> 00:31:48,920
Aren't doctors supposed to avoid sugar?

487
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:51,040
Except for this one person.

488
00:31:52,160 --> 00:31:53,320
Just this one person?

489
00:31:54,000 --> 00:31:54,760
Just one person.

490
00:31:54,760 --> 00:31:55,800
-Yeah.
-Okay.

491
00:31:56,600 --> 00:31:57,760
You sure?

492
00:31:57,760 --> 00:32:00,000
MOTHER

493
00:32:05,080 --> 00:32:06,200
Go answer your phone.

494
00:32:06,200 --> 00:32:07,640
The hospital is probably calling.

495
00:32:11,240 --> 00:32:12,840
Go answer the phone.

496
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:14,920
Go on.

497
00:32:24,160 --> 00:32:25,160
Hello, Mother.

498
00:32:26,720 --> 00:32:27,720
<i>At 10 o'clock, okay?</i>

499
00:32:28,040 --> 00:32:29,040
Okay.

500
00:32:29,800 --> 00:32:30,840
Don't be late.

501
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:33,480
Got it. See you tomorrow.

502
00:32:34,040 --> 00:32:35,040
Okay, dear.

503
00:32:35,560 --> 00:32:36,560
Bye, Mom.

504
00:32:44,320 --> 00:32:45,680
My child will not be tainted

505
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:46,840
by a woman like you.

506
00:33:01,880 --> 00:33:02,880
Earn,

507
00:33:04,280 --> 00:33:05,320
we’re here.

508
00:33:10,760 --> 00:33:11,920
It’s already so late,

509
00:33:11,920 --> 00:33:13,760
what time do you think you’ll finish?

510
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:17,960
I’m not sure.

511
00:33:18,440 --> 00:33:20,240
The team called me in last minute

512
00:33:20,240 --> 00:33:22,320
because the previous guest

513
00:33:22,360 --> 00:33:24,480
fell ill unexpectedly, I think.

514
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:26,640
They needed me to fill in,

515
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:28,920
and I didn’t want to let them down.

516
00:33:32,560 --> 00:33:33,760
Well,

517
00:33:34,600 --> 00:33:35,840
I’d better get to work.

518
00:33:36,160 --> 00:33:37,440
Drive home safely, okay?

519
00:33:38,120 --> 00:33:39,120
Of course.

520
00:33:42,840 --> 00:33:44,520
Thanks for the shirt, by the way.

521
00:33:45,120 --> 00:33:46,120
You’re welcome.

522
00:33:50,360 --> 00:33:51,360
Bye-bye.

523
00:33:56,480 --> 00:33:57,480
Bye-bye.

524
00:34:07,640 --> 00:34:08,639
Whoa!

525
00:34:10,280 --> 00:34:11,080
Amazing.

526
00:34:11,080 --> 00:34:12,159
Hey,

527
00:34:12,400 --> 00:34:14,280
you know the line-up with Engfah is

528
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,159
now booked for 3-4 months straight?

529
00:34:16,159 --> 00:34:19,280
And your fee is 10 times the usual rate.

530
00:34:19,679 --> 00:34:20,920
You practically don’t have

531
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,000
to do anything else,

532
00:34:22,040 --> 00:34:24,040
just show up and collect the money.

533
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,600
Suzie,

534
00:34:26,440 --> 00:34:28,280
can’t I take other jobs

535
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:30,560
that don’t involve Engfah?

536
00:34:30,719 --> 00:34:31,719
What?

537
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:32,760
Why?

538
00:34:32,760 --> 00:34:34,159
Didn't you two sorted everything out?

539
00:34:34,199 --> 00:34:35,520
We did,

540
00:34:35,639 --> 00:34:37,280
but I’m worried about Doctor.

541
00:34:37,440 --> 00:34:38,520
And what about me,

542
00:34:38,560 --> 00:34:39,800
the one who books your jobs?

543
00:34:39,840 --> 00:34:41,239
Oh, Suzie,

544
00:34:41,400 --> 00:34:42,880
you know that there’s nothing

545
00:34:42,920 --> 00:34:44,360
between me and Engfah,

546
00:34:44,360 --> 00:34:45,880
but the people hiring us

547
00:34:45,920 --> 00:34:49,000
want that cute, couple-like vibe.

548
00:34:49,040 --> 00:34:50,040
You get?

549
00:34:50,480 --> 00:34:52,320
I don’t want to mislead them.

550
00:34:52,520 --> 00:34:54,320
Oh, Miss Goody-Two-Shoes,

551
00:34:54,560 --> 00:34:55,400
Look,

552
00:34:55,400 --> 00:34:56,920
not everyone has a rich doctor

553
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:58,160
for a girlfriend like you.

554
00:34:58,200 --> 00:34:59,800
I can’t be as choosy with work.

555
00:35:00,360 --> 00:35:03,280
Suzie, I’m sorry.

556
00:35:03,400 --> 00:35:04,880
I won’t complain about anything else.

557
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:06,360
Look, I came here as soon

558
00:35:06,400 --> 00:35:08,400
as they called, no complaints.

559
00:35:08,680 --> 00:35:11,240
Just this one thing, please?

560
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:12,840
Please, Suzie.

561
00:35:13,040 --> 00:35:15,280
If you don’t, I’ll kiss your cheek!

562
00:35:16,280 --> 00:35:18,800
Eek! Go away!

563
00:35:22,840 --> 00:35:23,720
Are you crazy?

564
00:35:23,760 --> 00:35:25,000
-Will you agree?
-No.

565
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:26,040
Please?

566
00:35:26,040 --> 00:35:27,080
I beg you.

567
00:35:27,240 --> 00:35:28,240
Please?

568
